---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="w-full py-14 bg-subtle text-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
            <div>
                <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
                    <img src="/images/logo-liderazap.png" alt="LideraZap" class="h-10 w-auto"/>
                </a>
                <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--text-muted)] max-w-sm">
                    Loja no WhatsApp, gestão de redes e presença online feita por especialistas. Sem complicação, direto ao ponto.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Navegação</h4>
                <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-[15px]">
                    <li><a href="#servicos" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Serviços</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#sobre" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Sobre</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#avaliacoes" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Avaliações</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contato" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Contato</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Redes</h4>
                <div class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-4">
                    <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram" class="text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        <iconify-icon icon="mdi:instagram" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook" class="text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        <iconify-icon icon="mdi:facebook" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="YouTube" class="text-[var(--text-muted)] hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        <iconify-icon icon="mdi:youtube" width="26" height="26"></iconify-icon>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-6 text-center text-[var(--text-muted)]">
            &copy; {year} LideraZap. Todos os direitos reservados.
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>